The paper discusses a reinforcement learning approach using policy gradient methods and neural networks for high-dimensional continuous control tasks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Among these, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely categories as they are directly related to the paper's focus on reinforcement learning and neural networks. cs.RO is also a likely category given the application of the approach to locomotion tasks for simulated robots. cs.NE and cs.CV are less likely categories, but still possible given the use of neural networks in the approach.
